@startuml
title Singleton

skinparam legendBackgroundColor #f9f9f9
skinparam legendBorderColor #999999

legend right
**Intent**: Ensure a class has only one instance and provide a global access point.

**Use when**: Shared resources, configuration, registries.

**Note**: Beware of testability and hidden dependencies.
endlegend

class Singleton {
  -instance : Singleton
  -Singleton()
  +getInstance() : Singleton
}

note right of Singleton
Private constructor
Static global accessor
Thread-safety considerations
end note
@enduml